        <div class="msgSubject"><img src="http://common.zam.com/shared/sticky_ico.gif" height="16" width="16" alt=""/> So... you want to be a miner?</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-08-25 02:08:04 | Edited: Nov 15 2010  5:44pm  | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1282723684112701255" id="quote-1282723684112701255" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1282723684112701255" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=219&amp;mid=1282723684112701255&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1282723684112701255&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1282723684112701255" onclick="followToggle('add','1282723684112701255')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
