      <div class="msgContentFrame">Couple of things <br /> <br />1) Sharp vision does indeed need to be set. Its under the last set of ability slot (passive i think? Not in game atm). Try waiting abit, there was a massive amount of lag when i set it and nearly closed the window thinking it was something automatic. When set it will randomly kick in when mining a spot, usually around the last few digs from what ive seen. Never seen it kick in at the start. <br /> <br />2) The lowest amount of swings ive seen is 2. It appears to depend on you rank, and the rank of the item being dug up <br /> <br />3) Ive found level 2 nodes around camp horizon near Ul'Dah, looking for rank 3 ones now. Also found the occasional rank 5 whilst running about exploring.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>FFXIV WUTAI  <br />Hayley Williams <br />Miner <br /> <br />FFXI SLYPH <br />Anikal <br />Nin Pup</div></div>
